    "input": "*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: C:\\Users\\nilay\\.copilot\\session-state\\cc097ede-7653-47f2-b9f0-b8d23d51d0d6\\plan.md\n+## Plan\n+\n+1. Read the notification preference route, existing notification-related rules, shared types, and frontend preference UI/API surfaces.\n+2. Implement a pure backend event-channel validator that reuses the existing mandatory-event and LEGAL-218 rule logic.\n+3. Add focused unit tests for valid combinations, mandatory-event failures, and California SMS false-positive/hard-negative coverage.\n+4. Wire the validator into the notification preference write route and then review the edited files for consistency.\n*** End Patch\n",
